messages.speech:
JEE Mains is a pan-India entrance examination, conducted for admission into top NITs (National Institutes of Technology), IIITs (Indian Institutes of Information Technology) and a few other state-funded universities.
The JEE Mains is also considered as a qualifying examination for the JEE Advanced. For more information about the colleges accepting JEE Mains Score, you can visit- https://www.shiksha.com/b-tech/jee-main-exam
